        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div id="crawler-form" class="card w-full max-w-md">
            <div class="mb-6 text-center">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Nuevo proyecto</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Ingresa la URL que deseas procesar</p>
            </div>
            
            <form class="space-y-6">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="projectName" class="block text-sm font-medium">
                  Nombre del proyecto
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="projectName"
                  name="projectName"
                  placeholder="Mi Proyecto"
                  required
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-tuatara-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tuatara-primary/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="url" class="block text-sm font-medium">
                  URL del sitio web
                </label>
                <input
                  type="url"
                  id="url"
                  name="url"
                  placeholder="https://ejemplo.com"
                  required
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-tuatara-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tuatara-primary/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="maxDepth" class="block text-sm font-medium">
                  Profundidad máxima
                </label>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <input
                    type="range"
                    id="maxDepth"
                    name="maxDepth"
                    min="1"
                    max="5"
                    value="3"
                    class="w-full"
                  />
                  <span id="maxDepthValue" class="w-8 text-center">3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <label for="maxPages" class="block text-sm font-medium">
                  Páginas máximas
                </label>
                <select
                  id="maxPages"
                  name="maxPages"
                  class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-tuatara-primary focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tuatara-primary/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800"
                >
                  <option value="10">10 páginas</option>
                  <option value="25">25 páginas</option>
                  <option value="50">50 páginas</option>
                  <option value="100" selected>100 páginas</option>
                  <option value="200">200 páginas</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-full">
                Iniciar procesamiento
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Features section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container px-4">
      <div class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Características principales</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
          MailBot ofrece un conjunto de herramientas para procesar sitios web
          y generar respuestas inteligentes para tus leads.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-tuatara-primary/10 text-tuatara-primary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 11.5a7 7 0 1 1 14 0 7 7 0 0 1-14 0Z"></path><path d="M18 11.5a7 7 0 0 1-14 0"></path><path d="m9 9-2 2"></path><path d="m15 9 2 2"></path><path d="M9 9a3 3 0 0 1 6 0"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Crawling inteligente</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Recorre automáticamente los sitios web, descubriendo y procesando todas las páginas relevantes.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-design-primary/10 text-design-primary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><path d="M10 13H8"></path><path d="M16 13h-4"></path><path d="M10 17H8"></path><path d="M16 17h-4"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Conversión a Markdown</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Convierte automáticamente el contenido HTML en markdown limpio y estructurado.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-marketing-primary/10 text-marketing-primary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Generación de embeddings</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Crea vectores semánticos para cada fragmento de contenido, permitiendo búsquedas avanzadas.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 4 -->
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-development-primary/10 text-development-primary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12c0-4.97-4.03-9-9-9s-9 4.03-9 9 4.03 9 9 9 9-4.03 9-9Z"></path><path d="M15 9.4a4 4 0 1 0 0 5.2"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Respuestas inteligentes</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Genera respuestas automáticas para tus leads basadas en el contenido procesado.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 5 -->
        <div class="card flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-tuatara-secondary/10 text-tuatara-secondary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"></path><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Personalización avanzada</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Configura cómo se procesan las páginas, qué elementos se ignoran y cómo se generan las respuestas.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 6 -->
        <!-- <div class="card flex flex-col">
